WEBVTT

05:17.775 --> 05:19.193
You hear me?

11:55.631 --> 11:57.133
Thank you very much, Mom.

12:05.599 --> 12:06.642
Hi. What's up?

12:24.702 --> 12:26.620
Ma, what's wrong?

12:38.048 --> 12:42.052
I have to pack.
They need me on set this week.

12:46.599 --> 12:51.103
Calgary. You hate the cold.
What are you going to do in Calgary?

12:51.187 --> 12:54.940
I'll buy a big coat.

12:55.024 --> 12:59.111
You see, son? Today we have all won.

13:13.542 --> 13:16.462
Say goodbye to Hayley for me.
Tell her I love her. I love you.

13:16.545 --> 13:17.463
Love you a lot, Mama.

35:59.323 --> 36:01.159
Congratulations,
blonde ex-wife.

36:01.742 --> 36:04.162
Thank you, crazy ex-husband.
